Darkness Radio presents Psi-Kids and MindPower Techniques with Psychic/Medium/Teacher Elly Molina!

On today's show, we sit down with Elly to talk about how to tell if a child has psychic abilities, developing those psychic abilities, and go into Elly's own rich history as well, including training with with an Israeli/Morrocan Chazah, and her time working as a psychic for California Psychics!
